<Layout title="Offline" description="You're currently offline.">
  <h1>You're offline</h1> 
  <p>You're not connected to the internet 🙁. Pages you've already visited are saved should still load. Reconnect and reload to keep browsing new content.</p>
  <p><button type="button" onclick="location.reload()">Try again</button></p>
</Layout>